
Blade  

Based on Novacoin
Proof of Work/Proof of Stake Hybrid-- Updated as of March 30 2014 over 90% of the Proof of Work coins have been produced
The Network will soon be 100% proof of stake
10 day minimum /30 days for full weight to receive proof of stake payment
The minimum pay outs are set low so many 'smaller' payments will be made to those holding coins at the rate of 100% interest per year
The block spacing is 5 minutes to provide stability
This project was inspired by the classic science fiction movie Blade Runner
****UNLIKE OTHER PROOF OF STAKE PROJECTS YOU MUST HAVE YOUR WALLET OPEN TO GENERATE AND RECEIVE PROOF OF STAKE PAYMENTS+++++




